Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:119,119}Intro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:8919,10919}{\i1}I fell in love with someone\Nfor the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:12119,18452}{\i1}I met him when he was looking for my\Ngrandma's wallet, not afraid to get his hands dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:18452,23386}{\i1}I still remember his smile\Nwhen he finally found the wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:25752,29786}{\i1}I will never forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:33186,36052}{\i1}He was dressed\Nlike a Buddhist monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:36952,39052}{\i1}I would like to meet him\Nagain so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:41019,42552}{\i1}One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:64552,69752}Although connected to this world,\Nthey do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:69752,74119}Although connected to that world,\Nthey do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:74119,79252}Anger, revenge, malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:79252,84952}No matter what form evil takes,\Nthey shall get rid of it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:84952,88486}The guardian deities of the modern world:\Nthe Pi-hyoro family!
Comment: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:28.48,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:88486,88486}Opening
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:34.18,Default,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:89719,94186}{\blur0.5\move(320,400,320,385)\an5\fs33\t(0,5000,\fscx90\fscy90)\1c&H78D5F1&\bord0}The Guardian Deities of Our Time\N{\1c&H615DBA&\3c&HB4B0D0&\bord5\fs60\fnDoubledecker DEMO}The Pi-hyoro family!
Comment: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:51.01,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:171019,171019}Main part
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171719,174986}You really can't stay\Nany longer, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174986,178619}It was my last funeral for today,\Nso I'll be on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178986,183919}Please don't be such a formalist.\NIf you stay, I'll make you dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183919,187986}I'm afraid that when it comes to dinner, my sister\Nis already waiting for me at home with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184619,187419}{\an8}Please stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187986,189152}Just a little longer, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189152,191386}Thank you for your\Nhospitality. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191386,193386}Ah, sensei…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194219,199886}What's with all those widows\Nthat they're into monks so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204619,206619}An accident?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.88,0:03:38.58,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:210886,218586}{\blur10\bord0\t(0,1500,\blur0)\fad(1000,1500)}"A Maze of Snow"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:40.65,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:216819,220652}{\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&\t(0,1500,\1c&HA5DFFF&\3c&H202020&\4c&H202020&)}Hōnenji Temple
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218786,220652}Welcome home, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222419,226919}By the way, do you already\Nhave plans for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226919,232252}You bet. I'm going with a friend from school\Nto the Christmas concert of Otometai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232252,234952}And I think Kibatta-neechan\Nand Kyūta-niichan will go on dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234952,237486}Well, well. I didn't know\Nthey had lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237486,242619}I can understand Kyūta, but Kibatta-neesan?\NWell, I guess she's in the right age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242619,244319}So who is the chosen one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244319,245919}Kariya-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245919,248652}You know, that guy\Nfrom Ruōgi Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248886,251686}Ah, Ikuhashi's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254052,256419}How about you, Kyōta-niichan?\NAre you going on a date, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258052,261786}He has as much to do with dates\Nas chalk and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261786,264386}Have you ever seen him\Nto go on one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264552,266752}But he is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267819,269319}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269319,271319}All the neighborhood women\Nhave hots for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272619,275252}Well, but you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275252,281019}Our bro has never been with anyone.\NHe's just totally at odds with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282219,284952}Don't tease him like that,\NKyonta-niichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284952,286319}But it's all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293952,297419}Oh, Kyōta-niichan, I mean, as a manly dude,\Nyou don't care about such stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297419,299419}Ah, yes. I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299419,300086}Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301186,306119}In the end I am at odds with the girls.\NWhat do I know about love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311652,312986}He took it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312986,314419}It's time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314419,317119}I think I left the stove on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321119,324119}Kyonta, that bonehead.\NSo what if I've never been on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324886,327252}There are many other things\Nthat excite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330386,332052}{\i1}Something that excites me…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337652,339752}There is nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:47.75,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:343752,347752}Nakazato
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344552,347752}Oh, it's you, Junko-san.\NHave you come to pay respect to Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348919,354119}When I saw you in that uniform,\NI thought for a moment that it was Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354119,357052}I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357052,359186}No, no, child.\NI'm making a show of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359186,361419}Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361419,365486}Introduce Kyōta-niichan to a girl?\NWhat's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365486,369052}Kyūta-niichan,\Nyou know a lot of girls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369052,373319}Even if I was to give each one of my limbs,\NI couldn't satisfy everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373319,375119}See? That's what\NI'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375119,378419}Our brother is a total loser\Nin that regard. Let's help him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378419,380419}Please.\NIt's a piece of cake for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386452,389219}I'm so sorry, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392952,398719}If I hadn't asked you to help me run this\Nstupid errand, you'd be still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412919,414452}{\i1}Junko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415186,417152}{\i1}Junko…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417152,419452}Shi… Shinobu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419452,421319}{\i1}I want to meet him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421319,423819}{\i1}I told you about him, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423819,426152}{\i1}The one I liked so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427686,432486}{\i1}I'd so love to see him again.\NTo tell him how i feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432486,435986}{\i1}Junko, we're best friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436786,439086}{\i1}I don't think you'll be mad
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439086,441752}{\i1}if I borrow your body for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441752,443852}{\i1}Right, Junko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459119,460319}Junko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461086,463052}Junko-san,\Nis everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466086,467952}Junko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468119,471352}I'm fine, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471352,475019}Good. Please wait a moment,\NI'll make us some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481886,485486}Now I can go and meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489252,490986}Kyōta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492419,496186}Hey, Kyūta. Where are you\Ndragging me to, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496186,498752}Oh? Ah, yes.\NHow do I say it…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498752,501986}To a place where Christmas\Nstarts a little earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512119,513919}Hey, Kyūta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518586,521619}{\i1}You're here, my prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523186,525452}Hi, Kyū-chan!\NI missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525452,526852}Wait, Sayako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526852,530752}– Oh, Kyūta-kun, I want one, too!\N– You didn't forget about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531752,534652}And who is this boy?\NKyū-chan, is he your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534652,537452}That's my brother, Kyōta-niichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537452,539719}Kyū-chan, that's your brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539719,542986}– How handsome!\N– Yeah, very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544319,547419}Oh, something is\Nstuck to your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547419,549519}I'll remove it for you.\NLean forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549519,551052}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551052,552952}The first kiss belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567019,568419}Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570452,572619}That's not fair, Sayako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572619,574152}Now, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579119,580519}What… what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580519,582519}What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587119,591786}{\i1}That stupid girl…\NShe kissed him before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593252,594752}{\i1}She will regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596819,598719}Wait up, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598719,600586}Be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600586,602719}Hey! Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616352,618486}A m… murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626186,628052}You can still feel a tiny bit of aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628052,629719}Can this be…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633452,634452}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635719,637652}To Kyōta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641252,644552}Not just that.\NIt's from a high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644552,647719}Holy moly!\NIt's a love letter, Kyōta-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647719,649819}Listen, Kyonta…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654219,658119}"I watched you all the time." See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658119,660586}Our exorcist brother\Nfinally got an admirer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660586,661952}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664219,666719}That's her? Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666719,667919}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667919,669819}Show it, show it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669819,671652}Hey, she's quite a looker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671652,673519}What a cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673519,675486}Continuing on…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675486,678619}"I would like to ask you something\Nand I hope you will agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678619,682952}If you have time in the evening of\NDecember 24, maybe we could meet… "
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682952,685352}Dude, she's totally\Ninviting you on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685352,688352}On the night of Christmas Eve, on top of it.\NYou can't screw this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689986,692686}– Who said I was going?\N– You have nothing to do anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692686,695619}Apparently you've forgotten\Nthat I got to help with the funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695619,700352}Kyōta! Do you have any idea how much\Ncourage it cost this girl to write this letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700352,703452}Isn't she cute?\NIsn't she brave?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703452,705452}And you don't care\Nabout any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707552,710052}Go and have a little fun.\NIt'll be a good experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710052,713252}You've always been too serious.\NIt's a great chance for you to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713652,714752}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715719,718219}Awesome! Kyōta-niichan,\Nit's your first date!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720919,722519}I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722519,724019}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724019,725686}Hey, how have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725686,728119}We haven't talked\Non the phone for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731019,731652}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733452,735219}Sayako was murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737619,739419}{\i1}Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739419,742019}{\i1}My poor Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742019,744686}{\i1}Your anger was just.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744686,752686}{\i1}But as long as Kyōta is alive,\Nmore women will appear in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752686,754152}I will kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754152,757219}I'll kill them, like I killed that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758386,760519}{\i1}There is a better method.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760519,763319}{\i1}Kill Kyōta. Kill only him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763319,767719}{\i1}That way, he will\Nbelong only to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768386,769652}Only to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769652,773786}{\i1}Yes. No one else\Nwill be able to have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773786,776886}{\i1}By erasing him from this world,\Nyou will protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776886,779186}I shall kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785052,787786}This necktie might be\Na bit too flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788319,791286}But it's your first date.\NIt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791286,795119}Thanks for your help, Kyūta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795119,797652}After what happened to my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797652,800419}somehow I don't feel\Nlike going to parties anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800786,802919}Was it one of those disco girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804952,806686}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807419,811152}Kyōta-niichan, this is your first date!\NDon't think about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812052,814152}Yes. You look great.\NGo get her, tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814719,818052}{\i1}How are things?\NIs everything going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818052,821419}{\i1}Yes sir. Our brother has already\Ncome into contact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821419,824819}{\i1}Don't underestimate them. Although\Nthey haven't regained their memories yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824819,827719}{\i1}they are still incarnations\Nof the guardian deities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827719,833186}{\i1}I understand that perfectly. That is why\Nwe must eliminate Kyōta before it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:14:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833686,840419}{\i1}Without him, their power\Nshould drop significantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845586,847652}What a crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847919,850952}I'm not surprised.\NOtometai rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851352,854819}Let me give you the tickets\Nwhile there's still some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856119,860552}Oh gosh, instead of tickets,\NI took Kyōta-niichan's love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860552,863619}Only you could do it.\NYou'd mistake keys for an elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863619,867119}By the way, my brother is around here\Nsomewhere. It's his first date!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867119,868619}His first date?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868619,870219}He's a legendarily late bloomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870219,872452}It's kind of rare these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873019,874952}Do you wanna see his girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874952,877252}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877252,878652}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878652,880052}She's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880052,881552}She has western beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881552,883186}Her name is\NNakazato Shinobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887019,891919}It's so relaxing when we sit here\Nand just talk quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891919,894719}I think they call it "feeling\Nbutterflies in the stomach".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896052,898752}Is everything okay on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899219,901752}Yes. I told them\Nyou said "hi".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902186,904352}And how are your brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904352,906119}Annoying as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906119,908119}That means they're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915586,917086}Uhm, Ryōko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917086,920886}I think it may be a bit rude\Nto mention it so early,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920886,924352}but would you… uh…\NWould you mind if you and I…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924352,927186}Would you like to date me knowing\Nthat some day I'd like to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927652,930352}What? That's Nakazato Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930352,931686}You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931686,933519}Why would I kid you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933519,936486}Well, because Nakazato\NShinobu is sort of dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936486,937186}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937186,941186}She recently died\Nin a traffic accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942019,943719}Are you cold, Shinobu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943719,946186}Come again?\NAh, no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950119,952219}I don't think it'll stop\Nsnowing anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955219,957719}I'm plenty happy just by\Ngetting to meet you, Kyōta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958086,962119}See, I thought that\Nyou wouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974052,975719}Is everything okay, Shinobu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977486,978886}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979719,982419}I'm a terrible klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982419,984486}I still can't believe\Nthis is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984486,985852}I feel like I'm dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986686,989352}Come on, let's get a bite to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993086,996119}Hello? Ah, it's you, Kyonta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996119,998119}What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006619,1008386}I'm sorry, Shinobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008386,1013052}I'm not very good at talking.\NAren't you bored with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013052,1016886}Oh, knock it off. I'm the one\Nwho keeps babbling all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016886,1019652}I wouldn't put it that way.\NBesides, it's even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023352,1024319}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031519,1032519}Kyōta-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033919,1035619}What is it, Shinobu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038386,1039786}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043352,1048652}I'm sorry to spring this on you, but\Nit's been on my mind since I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048652,1050586}Kariya-sensei…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055086,1056252}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056252,1057552}Stampy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057552,1058686}Stamp…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060586,1063952}I think one of my brothers\Nneeds help. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063952,1065186}Ryōko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066186,1067819}We'll talk about it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069819,1072819}Slow down, Stampy!\NI don't have wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073186,1075586}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:18:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075586,1080986}So you're suggesting that Nakazato Shinobu is\Na ghost and she possessed her friend Junko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080986,1082152}We think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082152,1086452}But somehow she managed to suppress her\Naura and we were unable to locate her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086452,1089552}We also tried to sense where\NKyōta-niichan is, but to no avail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089552,1092286}Love is able to affect\Nthe default aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092286,1095352}But I don't think this girl's\Nghost has such power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095619,1098352}Either way, we have to find Kyōta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105686,1107119}There's nobody around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108452,1110852}That's why we came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115152,1118886}The pills should start\Nto work, Kyōta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119752,1120886}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121152,1127386}Are you getting hotter?\NCan you feel your strength being drained?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132086,1133652}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163786,1166052}{\i1}Well done, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166052,1168352}{\i1}Now Kyōta is only yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168719,1170619}Only mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171419,1174819}{\i1}Yes. Thus, you\Nfulfilled your goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177652,1180519}I'd love to hear more\Nabout these goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182586,1186319}You drove a girl who was in love with my brother\Nto the point that she wanted to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186319,1190152}You don't deserve anything.\NIt's over, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190352,1196386}{\i1}You all are such fools. Your entire family.\NWhat will you do without your beloved Kyōta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196652,1198652}What did you do to our brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200119,1205152}{\i1}His soul is now wandering around,\Non its way to the hereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208586,1211452}You're not just\Nany demon, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211452,1216152}{\i1}Well done, Avalokita Ema.\NI know that you are the chosen ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217352,1219252}You know that name?\NIt means that…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219252,1224386}{\i1}I am one of five Ninshū\Nwho were sealed long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224752,1226652}So you come from Chūkyō.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229519,1234552}{\i1}You are the last obstacle that\Nseparates us from true freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238819,1240352}{\i1}Open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240352,1242352}{\i1}Open your eyes, deity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243286,1247319}{\i1}Try to remember.\NRemember who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247319,1251719}{\i1}Remember the sword\Nthat this hand held.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252752,1254919}My… sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254919,1256619}{\i1}Yes. Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256852,1259052}My sword! Aśarañtr.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264386,1267952}{\i1}The four of you are the future\Nincarnation of the guardian deities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267952,1272319}{\i1}You are not a challenge for me.\NKyōta was the only one who could threaten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272319,1274319}{\i1}This is your end!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277852,1279886}I wouldn't be so sure\Nabout that, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279886,1281419}{\i1}Who… Who is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281986,1284986}Although connected to this world,\Nwe do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284986,1288686}Although connected to that world,\Nwe do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288686,1292119}Anger, revenge, malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292119,1296286}No matter what form evil takes,\Nwe shall get rid of it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296286,1297452}That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297452,1298719}{\i1}It's you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301752,1304419}The guardian deities\Nof the modern world,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304419,1306852}the Pi-hyoro family,\Nis ready for action!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309486,1312019}{\i1}Kyōta! You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312019,1314719}{\i1}Go on, Shinobu.\NKill this worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:22:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317419,1320252}{\i1}This time do not mess it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321352,1324719}Shinobu-chan, open your eyes.\NHe is deceiving you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326052,1331519}{\i1}It's pointless. As long as I am here,\Nher soul cannot hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331519,1333719}I want to protect you.\NI don't want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335286,1337719}Shinobu-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349119,1351119}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351986,1354652}From the moment I saw you\Nfor the first time…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356919,1360919}I've been thinking about you\Nover and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363419,1364419}Shinobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.45,0:22:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1365452,1368386}No. I can't kill you.\NI don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.81,0:22:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1368819,1370552}{\i1}Do as I say, Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370552,1372319}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372986,1374052}Shinobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1374052,1376319}Run, Kyōta-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1401486,1404986}{\i1}Stupid girl. That's what happens\Nto everyone who opposes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407852,1409252}You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1411452,1412819}– Kyōta!\N– Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412819,1414186}– Let's go.\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1421752,1422719}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1422952,1424652}{\i1}Haven't you had enough yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1424652,1426652}Lend me your energy, sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427952,1429786}Aśarañtr!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1439919,1441919}{\i1}How… Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1441919,1445586}{\i1}How did you recover\Nyour divine sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1447019,1448719}{\i1}How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.01,0:24:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1468019,1470052}Kyōta-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.05,0:24:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1470052,1472419}Kyōta, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.61,0:24:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1475619,1479852}Their memories still haven't\Nfully returned, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.85,0:24:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1479852,1482252}He managed to recover his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.25,0:24:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1482252,1484452}The rest is only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.58,0:24:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1484586,1489952}Yes. They managed to destroy one of Ninshū.\NI don't feel the aura of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.41,0:24:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1490419,1493886}They must've gotten the wind of his defeat\Nand ran away in fear of Pi-hyoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.88,0:24:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1493886,1496952}I am more than sure that they\Nwill make their appearance soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.78,0:25:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1497786,1500419}I think Ema may not be\Nall that willing to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.21,0:25:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1501219,1502252}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.25,0:25:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1502252,1503819}Archbishop Galius?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.81,0:25:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1503819,1506486}{\i1}I fear that a new battle\Nwill break out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.31,0:25:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1515319,1518219}I'm sorry, Ryōko-san.\NI got held up by the patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.08,0:25:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1551086,1552919}{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.88,0:25:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1553886,1556119}{\i1}Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.11,0:25:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1556119,1558119}{\i1}Junko-chan.
Comment: 0,0:26:24.81,0:26:24.81,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1584819,1584819}Ending
Comment: 0,0:29:47.95,0:29:47.95,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1787952,1787952}Epilogue
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.95,0:29:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1787952,1789752}Hey. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.75,0:29:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1789752,1793619}I am Pi-hyoro Kyōta.\NHow did you like our show?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.61,0:29:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1793619,1797819}I am Shinohara Ryōko.\NI'm a bit ashamed to break the fourth wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.81,0:30:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1797819,1802786}Howdy! I am Kyonta. I won't let\Nmy brothers get too far ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.78,0:30:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1802786,1807652}My name is Pi-hyoro Kyūta.\NThank you for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.65,0:30:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1807652,1811552}We still have a lot to do, most of which\Nis about dealing with nasty demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.55,0:30:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1811552,1814786}The four of us will do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.78,0:30:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1814786,1816252}Will you support us?
